title: What a Mac mini and Tailscale enables
Cloud Object Storage Challenges?
text:
What challenges are you facing with Cloud object storage?

a) Cost - picking right storage class, duplicate content etc.

b) Performance - picking the right location, caching etc

c) Governance - access control, observability etc.

d) Something else

title: YouTube giveaway shipping cost scam
text:
Telegram Messages purporting to be from YT channel:

Are you aware that am running a giveaway for my subscribers on my channel?..

I am now

We selected our lucky shortlisted winners randomly from the comment section

You must be very lucky to be selected among our lucky shortlisted winners then

What's your full name?..

You won a Sony A7III, M1pro mac book, One hoodie and 2 limited edition stickers

You must be very lucky to be selected among our lucky shortlisted winners

What's your shipping address and postal code

I'll get the shipping company available to your location

After you have received your package to your location you will do a video or photo with your package and send it to us for confirmation that all our winner's has received their packages to their various locations

Is that okay by you?..

Hold on while my logistics manager process your details

These are the cost of shipping to your location select the one that suit you best.

[Image not available] Cost ranging from $140 to $205.

Those are international rates. Please quote domestic rates.

All shipping is placed on International rates
